    <fr:p>An orthonormal subset <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\\{e_\\lambda\\}_{\\lambda \\in \\Lambda}]]></fr:tex> of a <fr:link type="external" href="pre-Hilbert">pre-Hilbert</fr:link> <fr:link type="external" href="space">space</fr:link> <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[H]]></fr:tex> is maximal if 
the <fr:em>only</fr:em> vector <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u \in  H]]></fr:tex> satisfying <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\\langle u, e_\\lambda \\rangle = 0]]></fr:tex> for all <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\lambda  \in  \Lambda ]]></fr:tex> is <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[u = 0]]></fr:tex>.</fr:p>
    <fr:p>(It is an <fr:link type="external" href="orthonormal%20set">orthonormal set</fr:link>)</fr:p>
